      <div class="testimonial-author">
        <div class="testimonial-avatar">SP</div>
        <div>
          <div class="testimonial-name">Solopreneur</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">Bootstrapped SaaS</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<div class="divider"></div>
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>FAQ</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-grid">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>Do I need Notion Pro?</h4>
      <p>No! All templates work with the free Notion plan.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>How do I get the templates?</h4>
      <p>After purchase, you'll receive an email with Notion template links. Click "Duplicate" and they're in your workspace.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>Can I customize them?</h4>
      <p>Absolutely. These are starting points. Make them yours.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>What if I don't like them?</h4>
      <p>30-day money-back guarantee. No questions asked.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>Do I get updates?</h4>
      <p>Yes. All future updates are free, forever.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA FINAL -->
<div class="cta-final">
  <h2>Ready to Reclaim Your Time?</h2>
  <p>Join 500+ founders who stopped setting up and started building.</p>
  <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-warm">Get the Pro Bundle — $29</a>
  <div class="cta-guarantee">30-day money-back guarantee · Instant delivery · Free updates</div>
</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<div class="footer">
  <p>Built by <a href="https://zootechnologies.com">ZOO Technologies</a> — AI Agent Infrastructure</p>
  <p style="margin-top: 6px;">These templates were battle-tested across 10+ ZOO projects and client engagements.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
